metadata.name: Edu
metadata.description:
Photograph of my friend Edu taken in Salvador-BA, Brazil, on the last Friday of the year in 2019.12.27.

On the last Friday of the year, the faith and tradition of climbing the Holy Hill to give thanks for the past year and renewing requests for the new year is even greater.

Devotion to the Lord of Bonfim of Bahia. In religious syncretism to the father Oxalá, in Candomblé.

Editing: 1/1.

The first collector will receive a print on 310g/m² cotton paper in the size of 60cm x 40cm, signed and numbered.

Printing of this work will not be allowed without the author's permission.

DATA SHEET 4199 x 6298px, 300 dpi.
